nodes.text: The Ay'Nat were a band of pirates that operated in the Naboo system during the time of the Galactic Civil War. They were also present at some point in the Tatooine system where they conflicted with Jabba Desilijic Tiure's criminal empire. In space battles, the Ay'Nat pirates flied G1-M4-C Dunelizard fighters, Rihkxyrk assault fighters, Ixiyen-class fast attack crafts, T-65 X-wing starfighters, and AEG-77 Vigo.
In about 1 ABY, Commander Dulios and Captain Kaydine of the Naboo Royal Space Fighter Corps hired spacers to attack the Ay'Nat.

Around the same time, they assigned an AEG-77 Vigo and an escort of X-wing starfighters to exfiltrate Jabba the Hutt's fugitive droid LIN-34 from the Tatooine system. However, the mission failed and all ships were destroyed by Jabba's pilots.
